## How to Contribute

1. Fork the repository
2. Create a branch — `git checkout -b feature/your-feature`
3. Commit — `git commit -m "feat: describe what you did"`
4. Push — `git push origin feature/your-feature`
5. Open a Pull Request on GitHub

